{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I love trees, and I'm very lucky,"},{"time":3000,"text":"because we live near a wonderful arboretum,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and Sundays, usually, I'd go there with my wife"},{"time":9000,"text":"and now, with my four-year-old,"},{"time":11000,"text":"and we'd climb in the trees, we'd play hide and seek."},{"time":14000,"text":"The second school I was at had big trees too,"},{"time":18000,"text":"had a fantastic tulip tree, I think it was the biggest in the country,"},{"time":22000,"text":"and it also had a lot of wonderful bushes and vegetation"},{"time":26000,"text":"around it, around the playing fields."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"One day I was grabbed by some of my classmates,"},{"time":32000,"text":"and taken in the bushes -- I was stripped; I was attacked;"},{"time":36000,"text":"I was abused; and this came out of the blue."},{"time":41000,"text":"Now, the reason I say that, because, afterwards, I was thinking --"},{"time":45000,"text":"well, I went back into the school -- I felt dirty; I felt betrayed;"},{"time":51000,"text":"I felt ashamed, but mainly -- mainly, I felt powerless."},{"time":58000,"text":"And 30 years later I was sitting in an airplane,"},{"time":61000,"text":"next to a lady called Veronica, who came from Chile,"},{"time":64000,"text":"and we were on a human rights tour,"},{"time":67000,"text":"and she was starting to tell me what it was like to be tortured,"},{"time":72000,"text":"and, from my very privileged position,"},{"time":75000,"text":"this was the only reference point that I had."},{"time":79000,"text":"And it was an amazing learning experience"},{"time":81000,"text":"because, for me, human rights have been something in which I had,"},{"time":84000,"text":"you know, a part-time interest, but, mainly,"},{"time":87000,"text":"it was something that happened to other people over there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"But I got a phone call from Bono in 1985 and, as you know,"},{"time":97000,"text":"he's a great singer, but he's a magnificent hustler, and --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"(Laughter) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"a very hard guy to say no to, and he was saying,"},{"time":107000,"text":"you know, just after I'd done the Biko song,"},{"time":109000,"text":"we're going to do a tour for Amnesty,"},{"time":111000,"text":"you have to be on it, and really that was the first time"},{"time":114000,"text":"that I'd been out and started meeting people"},{"time":118000,"text":"who'd watched their family being shot in front of them,"},{"time":121000,"text":"who'd had a partner thrown out of an airplane into an ocean,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and suddenly this world of human rights arrived in my world,"},{"time":129000,"text":"and I couldn't really walk away in quite the same way as before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"So I got involved with this tour, which was for Amnesty,"},{"time":138000,"text":"and then in '88 I took over Bono's job trying to learn how to hustle."},{"time":143000,"text":"I didn't do it as well, but we managed to get Youssou N'Dour, Sting,"},{"time":147000,"text":"Tracy Chapman, and Bruce Springsteen to go 'round the world for Amnesty,"},{"time":152000,"text":"and it was an amazing experience."},{"time":155000,"text":"And, once again, I got an extraordinary education,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and it was the first time, really,"},{"time":161000,"text":"that I'd met a lot of these people in the different countries,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and these human rights stories became very physical,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and, again, I couldn't really walk away quite so comfortably."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"But the thing that really amazed me, that I had no idea,"},{"time":179000,"text":"was that you could suffer in this way"},{"time":182000,"text":"and then have your whole experience, your story, denied,"},{"time":188000,"text":"buried and forgotten."},{"time":191000,"text":"And it seemed that whenever there was a camera around,"},{"time":196000,"text":"or a video or film camera,"},{"time":199000,"text":"it was a great deal harder to do -- for those in power to bury the story."},{"time":206000,"text":"And Reebok set up a foundation after these Human Rights Now tours"},{"time":210000,"text":"and there was a decision then --"},{"time":214000,"text":"well, we made a proposal, for a couple of years,"},{"time":217000,"text":"about trying to set up a division"},{"time":219000,"text":"that was going to give cameras to human rights activists."},{"time":224000,"text":"It didn't really get anywhere,"},{"time":225000,"text":"and then the Rodney King incident happened, and people thought,"},{"time":228000,"text":"OK, if you have a camera in the right place at the right time,"},{"time":231000,"text":"or, perhaps, the wrong time, depending who you are,"},{"time":235000,"text":"then you can actually start doing something,"},{"time":240000,"text":"and campaigning, and being heard,"},{"time":244000,"text":"and telling people about what's going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"So, WITNESS was started in '92"},{"time":250000,"text":"and it's since given cameras out in over 60 countries."},{"time":256000,"text":"And we campaign with activist groups"},{"time":262000,"text":"and help them tell their story and, in fact,"},{"time":266000,"text":"I will show you in a moment one of the most recent campaigns,"},{"time":270000,"text":"and I'm afraid it's a story from Uganda,"},{"time":273000,"text":"and, although we had a wonderful story from Uganda yesterday,"},{"time":277000,"text":"this one isn't quite so good."},{"time":279000,"text":"In the north of Uganda,"},{"time":281000,"text":"there are something like 1.5 million internally displaced people,"},{"time":284000,"text":"people who are not refugees in another country,"},{"time":287000,"text":"but because of the civil war, which has been going on for about 20 years,"},{"time":291000,"text":"they have nowhere to live."},{"time":293000,"text":"And 20,000 kids have been taken away to become child soldiers,"},{"time":299000,"text":"and the International Criminal Court is going after five of the leaders of the --"},{"time":307000,"text":"now, what's it called?"},{"time":309000,"text":"I forget the name of the of the army --"},{"time":311000,"text":"it's Lord's Resistance Army, I believe --"},{"time":314000,"text":"but the government, also, doesn't have a clean sheet,"},{"time":316000,"text":"so if we could run the first video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":321000,"text":"Woman: Life in the camp is never simple. Even today life is difficult."},{"time":324000,"text":"We stay because of the fear that what pushed us into the camp ..."},{"time":328000,"text":"still exists back home."},{"time":334000,"text":"Text: \"Between Two Fires: Torture and Displacement in Northern Uganda\""},{"time":345000,"text":"Man: When we were at home, it was Kony's [rebel] soldiers disturbing us."},{"time":352000,"text":"At first, we were safe in the camp."},{"time":355000,"text":"But later the government soldiers began mistreating us a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"(Chanting)"},{"time":363000,"text":"Jennifer: A soldier walked onto the road, asking where we'd been."},{"time":367000,"text":"Evelyn and I hid behind my mother."},{"time":373000,"text":"Evelyn: He ordered us to sit down, so we sat down."},{"time":376000,"text":"The other soldier also came."},{"time":379000,"text":"Jennifer: The man came and started undressing me."},{"time":383000,"text":"The other one carried Evelyn aside."},{"time":386000,"text":"The one who was defiling me then left me and went to rape Evelyn."},{"time":391000,"text":"And the one who was raping Evelyn came and defiled me also."},{"time":395000,"text":"Man: The soldiers with clubs this long beat us to get a confession."},{"time":403000,"text":"They kept telling us, \"Tell the truth!\" as they beat us."},{"time":415000,"text":"Woman: They insisted that I was lying."},{"time":420000,"text":"At that moment, they fired and shot off my fingers."},{"time":425000,"text":"I fell. They ran to join the others ... leaving me for dead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":440000,"text":"Text: Uganda ratified the Convention Against Torture in 1986."},{"time":449000,"text":"Torture is defined as any act by which severe pain of suffering,"},{"time":453000,"text":"whether physical or mental,"},{"time":456000,"text":"is intentionally inflicted by a person acting in an official capacity"},{"time":460000,"text":"to obtain information or a confession, to punish, coerce or intimidate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"Peter Gabriel: So torture is not something that always happens on other soil."},{"time":474000,"text":"In my country, it was --"},{"time":476000,"text":"we had been looking at pictures of British soldiers beating up young Iraqis;"},{"time":483000,"text":"we've got Abu Ghraib; we've got Guantanamo Bay."},{"time":485000,"text":"I had a driver on my way to Newark Airport,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and he told me a story that, in the middle of the night, 4 a.m.,"},{"time":494000,"text":"he'd been taken out of his home in Queens -- taken to a place in the Midwest,"},{"time":500000,"text":"that he was interrogated and tortured"},{"time":504000,"text":"and returned to the street four weeks later,"},{"time":508000,"text":"because he had the same -- he was Middle Eastern,"},{"time":511000,"text":"and he had the same name as one of the 9/11 pilots,"},{"time":515000,"text":"and that may or may not be true --"},{"time":519000,"text":"I didn't think he was a liar, though."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522000,"text":"And, I think, if we look around the world,"},{"time":526000,"text":"as well as the polar ice caps melting,"},{"time":528000,"text":"human rights, which have been fought for,"},{"time":531000,"text":"for many hundreds of years in some cases,"},{"time":534000,"text":"are, also, eroding very fast,"},{"time":537000,"text":"and that is something that we need to take a look at"},{"time":541000,"text":"and, maybe, start campaigning for."},{"time":545000,"text":"I mean, here, too, one of our partners was at Van Jones"},{"time":550000,"text":"and the Books Not Bars project -- they have managed,"},{"time":554000,"text":"with their footage in California"},{"time":557000,"text":"to change the youth correction systems employed,"},{"time":562000,"text":"and it's much -- much -- I think, more humane methods"},{"time":567000,"text":"are being looked at, how you should lock up young kids,"},{"time":571000,"text":"and that's questionable to start off."},{"time":573000,"text":"And as the story of Mr. Morales, just down the road,"},{"time":579000,"text":"excuse me, Mr. Gabriel,"},{"time":581000,"text":"would you mind if we delayed your execution a little bit?"},{"time":585000,"text":"No, not at all, no problem, take your time."},{"time":588000,"text":"But this, surely, whoever that man is, whatever he's done,"},{"time":594000,"text":"this is cruel and unusual punishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598000,"text":"Anyway, WITNESS has been trying to arm the brave people"},{"time":604000,"text":"who often put their lives at risk around the world, with cameras,"},{"time":608000,"text":"and I'd like to show you just a little more of that. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"(Thunder) Text: You can say a story is fabricated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":623000,"text":"Text: You can say a jury is corrupt."},{"time":628000,"text":"You can say a person is lying."},{"time":635000,"text":"You can say you don't trust newspapers."},{"time":641000,"text":"But you can't say"},{"time":647000,"text":"what you just saw"},{"time":650000,"text":"never happened."},{"time":657000,"text":"Help WITNESS give cameras to the world."},{"time":662000,"text":"Shoot a video;"},{"time":671000,"text":"expose injustice;"},{"time":677000,"text":"reveal the truth;"},{"time":682000,"text":"show us what's wrong with the world;"},{"time":687000,"text":"and maybe"},{"time":689000,"text":"we can help"},{"time":691000,"text":"make it"},{"time":693000,"text":"right."},{"time":701000,"text":"WITNESS."},{"time":707000,"text":"All the video you have just seen was recorded by"},{"time":709000,"text":"human rights groups working with WITNESS."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":717000,"text":"PG: WITNESS was born of technological innovation --"},{"time":721000,"text":"in a sense the small, portable, DV cam"},{"time":723000,"text":"was really what allowed it to come into being."},{"time":727000,"text":"And we've also been trying to get computers out to the world,"},{"time":731000,"text":"so that groups can communicate much more effectively,"},{"time":733000,"text":"campaign much more effectively,"},{"time":735000,"text":"but now we have the wonderful possibility,"},{"time":741000,"text":"which is given to us from the mobile phone with the camera in it,"},{"time":745000,"text":"because that is cheap; it's ubiquitous; and it's moving fast"},{"time":750000,"text":"all around the world -- and it's very exciting for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"And so, the dream is that we could have a world"},{"time":757000,"text":"in which anyone who has anything bad happen to them of this sort"},{"time":763000,"text":"has a chance of getting their story uploaded,"},{"time":767000,"text":"being seen, being watched,"},{"time":770000,"text":"that they really know that they can be heard,"},{"time":773000,"text":"that there would be a giant website,"},{"time":777000,"text":"maybe, a little like Google Earth,"},{"time":779000,"text":"and you could fly over and find out the realities of what's going,"},{"time":783000,"text":"for the world's inhabitants. In a way"},{"time":786000,"text":"what this technology is allowing is, really,"},{"time":789000,"text":"that a lot of the problems of the world can have a human face,"},{"time":793000,"text":"that we can actually see who's dying of AIDS"},{"time":796000,"text":"or who's being beaten up, for the first time,"},{"time":801000,"text":"and we can hear their stories in a way that the blogger culture --"},{"time":805000,"text":"if we can move that into these sort of fields,"},{"time":808000,"text":"I think we can really transform the world in all sorts of ways."},{"time":815000,"text":"There could be a new movement growing up,"},{"time":819000,"text":"rising from the ground, reaching for the light,"},{"time":824000,"text":"and growing strong, just like a tree. Thank you."}]}]}